'''The Vice President of Ciskei''' was a political position in [[Ciskei|that republic]]. The Vice President was appointed as a deputy by the [[Heads of State of Ciskei|President]].<ref>http://letras.comp.filos.unam.mx/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/ColinWhite_TheRuleOfBrigadierOupaGqozoInCiskei.pdf</ref>
Rev. [[Willie Xaba]] held the office between December 1981 and 1983.<ref>''The Europa World Year Book 1985'', Volume II, p. 2593</ref><ref>https://www.sahistory.org.za/dated-event/chief-lennox-sebe-unanimously-elected-ciskeis-president-and-rev-wm-xaba-becomes-vice-pre</ref>
